1. *Predsednik* je izabran za šefa države. (The president was elected as the head of the state.)
2. *Predsednik* je bio izuzetno uspešan u svojoj dužnosti. (The president was extremely successful in his duty.)
3. *Predsednika* će narod nikada ne zaboraviti. (The people will never forget the president.)
4. *Predsednikova* politika je bila usmerena na napredak zemlje. (The president's policy was aimed at the progress of the country.)
5. *Predsedniku* su se mnogi ljudi obratili za pomoć. (Many people turned to the president for help.)